OL,6,FKent Police officers established that
OL,7,Fthe syndicate's level of success was
OL,8,Fnever sufficient to support the
OL,9,Fwithdrawals members were making or
OL,10,FStanley's own extravagant lifestyle,
OL,11,Fand evidence showed that at one point
OL,12,Fhe had lost over #1 million in
OL,13,Fgambling in a single year.
OL,15,FThey found Stanley was spending the
OL,16,Fmoney on 23 racehorses, a #400,000
OL,17,Fproperty in Spain, several new
OL,18,Fvehicles and expensive jewellery, and
OL,19,Fhe also bought #1.6 million of
OL,20,Fcryptocurrency and #622,000 worth of
OL,21,Fsilver bullion.
