OL,6,FStanley, of Resolution Road,
OL,7,FWalderslade, filed for bankruptcy in
OL,8,FJanuary 2019 shortly after allegations
OL,9,Fabout the legitimacy of the scheme
OL,10,Fwere published in a national newspaper.
OL,12,FHe was later charged with several
OL,13,Ffraud offences and pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fall ahead of his sentencing at
OL,15,FMaidstone Crown Court on Tuesday 24
OL,16,FSeptember 2024.
OL,18,FStanley was also made subject to a
OL,19,Ffive-year Serious Crime Prevention
OL,20,FOrder and disqualified from being a
OL,21,Fcompany director for 15 years.
