OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Alec Wood of Kent
OL,7,FPolice said: "Mike Stanley started
OL,8,FLayezy Racing in 2010 as a legitimate
OL,9,Fsource of income for himself and those
OL,10,Fwho paid into the scheme, but the
OL,11,Ffinancial evidence showed that from
OL,12,F2013 onwards he was criminally
OL,13,Fcheating people out of their hard-
OL,14,Fearned money in order to maintain his
OL,15,Fown lavish lifestyle.
