OL,6,F"In many cases his victims have
OL,7,Fexperienced a significant impact on
OL,8,Ftheir lives and financial futures as a
OL,9,Fresult of Stanley's false promises,
OL,10,Fand I would like to thank them for
OL,11,Ftheir assistance and patience with
OL,12,Fwhat was a significant case in terms
OL,13,Fof its scope, complexity and
OL,14,Fadministration.
OL,16,F"I hope the outcome of this
OL,17,Finvestigation sends a clear message
OL,18,Fthat anyone who seeks to lie and cheat
OL,19,Ftheir way to financial prosperity will
OL,20,Fbe brought to justice."
